West African peace-keeping force known as ECOMOG.
</P>
<P>
ECOMOG checkpoints have been removed from many places in
Liberian capital of Monrovia, since the inauguaration of the
Charles Taylor government that formally ended Liberia's seven
years of bloody civil war, the report said. 
