"Hong Kong people governing Hong Kong" and "a high degree of
autonomy", Jiang said that the Xinhua Hong Kong Branch will not
interfere with matters which fall in the domain of the high degree
of autonomy of the SAR government, but will cooperate with the SAR
government and support its work.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that Xinhua will maintain extensive contacts with
people in various walks of life in Hong Kong and continue its
efforts to enhance communication and interflow between the Hong
Kong SAR and other parts of the motherland so as to maintain the
long-term prosperity and stability of Hong Kong.  
