the biggest loser as it declined by 1.7 Singapore dollars to end
at 24.7 dollars. C Properties and the Overseas Chinese Banking
Corporation fell by one dollar each to close at 16.5 and 12.6
Singapore dollars respectively. The Singapore Airlines (SIA)
Foreign and the United Overseas Bank (UOB) Foreign each finished
80 cents lower at 11.6 and 12.9 Singapore dollars respectively.
