slender advantage for the return leg match as they edged over
Croatia Zagreb 2-1 through John Beresford's two strikes in either
half of the match.
</P>
<P>
Top French side Paris Saint Germain have to make most of their
return leg in France in two weeks' time after they went down 3-2
against Romanian champions Steaua Bucharest.
</P>
<P>
