Leverkusen thrashed Georgia's Dinamo Tbilisi 6-1, Barcelona earned
a narrow 3-2 home win over Latvia's Skonto Riga and Olympiakos of
Greece hammered FC Mozyr of Belarus 5-0 in Athens.
</P>
<P>
The minor upset took place in Cyprus, where the home favourite
Anorthosis Famagusta were cheered on to beat Belgian champions
Lierse 2-0. 
