<TEXT>
<P>
PANAMA CITY, August 13 (Xinhua) -- One student was slightly
injured and 15 were arrested today in the clashes between
Panamanian riot police and youths protesting possible plans to set
up a U.S.-assisted international anti-drug center in Panama.
</P>
<P>
The clashes took place outside the U.S. Embassy in Panama City.
</P>
