negotiations over the possibility of creating a Multilateral
Counternarcotics Center (MCC) at Howard Air Force Base.
</P>
<P>
Under bilateral canal treaties signed between Panama and the
United State, the United States will turn over control of the
Panama Canal to Panama and withdraw all troops and bases,
including the Howard base, by Dec. 31, 1999. 
